=== /etc/ppp/simyo-connect-chat ===
<pre>TIMEOUT 10
ABORT BUSY
ABORT DELAYED
ABORT "NO ANSWER"
ABORT "NO DIALTONE"
ABORT VOICE
ABORT ERROR
ABORT RINGING
TIMEOUT 30
'' ATZ
OK ATE1
OK AT+CFUN=1
ERROR AT+CPIN?
OK AT+COPS?
OK AT+CGDCONT=1,"IP","internet.eplus.de"
OK 'ATDT*99***1#'
CONNECT ''
</pre>


